  • Packages that use com.paydiant.android.core.enums.transactionflow 
    Package Description
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain
    Domain objects that is used to transfer data between the SDK and the mobile gateway.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain.splittender
    This package contains domain objects that can be used to perform operations on split tender transactions.
    com.paydiant.android.core.domain.transactionflow
    This package contains set of domain objects that can be used to provide support for transaction flows.
    com.paydiant.android.core.enums.transactionflow
    Defines a set of Enums that used with the transaction flow operations.
